Moving from New York to Miami, @iamspinelli , you have shown us all that it's possible to live out our dreams and persevere. 

It was great to catch up and learn that we actually have similar stories. 

From creating parties like Groove Theory and spinning at Everydayppl, to captivating renowned organizations like Apple Inc. and the NAACP, you have made big moves in the DJing community. 

Your journey is a testament that no matter where you come from, what you look like, or what resources you start with, as long as you commit to yourself, understand the process, and create with pure intention, the sky's the limit on how far you can go and what you can achieve. 

The @tresgentequila family applauds you. #getuptres
